The editor for the NFSv4 bis internet draft uses this site as a method of distributing content and issue tracking. The latest version of the NFSv4.0 I-D is always found on the IETF site. The NFSv4 WG page will have pointers to all of this and includes a pointer to the email archive as well.

http://www.ietf.org/html.charters/nfsv4-charter.html
http://www.ietf.org/mail-archive/web/nfsv4/index.html

NOTE: The drafts contained here may change after it is posted to the IETF site. The ITEF site is always the definitive authority on content.
